00:13:39,988 --> 00:13:43,449
CLARE:
Eu entrei.

344
00:13:43,533 --> 00:13:45,285
Eu entrei.
(Rindo)

345
00:13:45,368 --> 00:13:47,412
ALLI: Na Columbia?
